2480. Form a Chemical Bond

- Solution 1.

select 
      e1.symbol as metal, 
      e2.symbol as nonmetal
from Elements e1, Elements e2
where e1.type = 'Metal' 
and e2.type = 'Nonmetal'


- Solution 2.

select 
      e1.symbol as metal, 
      e2.symbol as nonmetal
from Elements e1
join Elements e2 
on e1.type = 'Metal' 
and e2.type = 'Nonmetal'
